downloadTitle: Hosting and Managed Services Partner Seller Readiness Handbook
downloadDescription: The Hosting and Managed Services Partner Seller Readiness Handbook provides guidance on how HMSP Partners can ready their sellers to sell Microsoft cloud services.
detailsSection: The Hosting and Managed Services Partner Seller Readiness Handbook provides guidance on how HMSP Partners can ready their sellers to sell Microsoft cloud services and links to supporting product, sales, and technical training guides and tools. This partner-facing document is updated monthly and is posted to internal team sites and shared directly with Partners via HMSP IMDM/CEs/Trainers/PM/Portals.
